Subject: RE: Netwrix Support Ticket #435989 - - 00435989 - How to Delete Old Computers [ ref:!00D70091pB.!500Qk0Lw0DM:ref ]

Hey Alex,

Thank you. While there is no filter, you can definitely sort as descending by the Last Seen column in the table and select the ones you want to remove.
Then at the bottom of the page, just press Delete.
Even if you remove a computer by mistake, as soon as it communicates with the server, it will be added back.
Let me know if you have follow-up questions, or if this can be closed.

Thank you,
